    <div class="section-label">What it is</div>
    <h2>A practical sales execution lab for real B2B selling.</h2>
    <p>Sales Execution Lab is built for teams that are already selling, prospecting, calling, following up, and trying to create pipeline — but the execution is not sharp enough yet.</p>
    <p>The problem is rarely one magic script. The real breakdown is usually a mix of weak openings, unclear value, passive follow-up, poor qualification, shaky objection handling, and inconsistent pipeline discipline.</p>
    <p>This lab helps your people improve the actual selling behavior that happens between first contact and qualified opportunity.</p>
  </div>
</section>

