  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">The real problem</div>
    <h2>Your team may not need more sales theory. They need better execution under pressure.</h2>
    <p>Most sales teams know they should call, follow up, ask better questions, handle objections, and move deals forward.</p>
    <p>But knowing it and doing it under pressure are not the same thing.</p>
    <p>Pipeline breaks when reps sound unsure, founders over-explain, follow-up gets weak, objections shut the conversation down, and nobody has a clear rhythm for moving the right prospects forward.</p>
    <div class="punch">Sales Execution Lab is built to fix the behavior, language, habits, and confidence behind stronger sales conversations.</div>
  </div>
